    "description": "Maverick Storm 1 Beam brings CMY color mixing and stadium-scale output in a lightweight compact alloy-armored IP65-rated fixture that delivers sharp beam effects and precise color. With an optical system designed to capture the full force of its SIRIUS HRI 310W source, this powerful beam fixture slices through every other effect. Tightly focused aerials and dual layerable independent prisms create massive visual effects, with frost to fine-tune looks and light distribution. Maverick Storm 1 Beam speaks DMX, ArtNet, sACN, RDM and W-DMX.",
